  "aboutTexts": [
    {
      "tag": "H2",
      "text": "Your Partner in Quality Home Care",
      "classes": "heading-style-h1 text-align-center"
    },
    {
      "tag": "P",
      "text": "At Serenica, our mission is to blend professionalism with heartfelt compassion. With a dedicated team and personalized approach, we ensure seniors receive the care and dignity they deserve—right at ho",
      "classes": "text-align-center text-color-secondary"
    },
    {
      "tag": "H3",
      "text": "Care That Honors Life, Values, and Family",
      "classes": "heading-style-h2"
    },
    {
      "tag": "P",
      "text": "We believe home care is more than assistance—it’s about preserving independence, respecting dignity, and nurturing the human connection. Every plan is shaped by listening to families and honoring the ",
      "classes": "text-color-secondary"
    },
    {
      "tag": "P",
      "text": "Every family and every senior has a unique story. That’s why we listen first, then build care plans that reflect not only health needs but also values, routines, and relationships that matter most.",
      "classes": "text-color-secondary"
    }
  ],
